headline: The Best Dividend Stock to Invest $1,000 in Right Now
summary: Prologis is the leader in logistics infrastructure REITs, with Amazon as its top client.  It has massive opportunities as e-commerce becomes more of a part of daily life.  Real estate investment trusts (REITs) make excellent dividend stocks because they pay out 90% of their earnings as dividends.
